Third-party assets and model notices
------------------------------------

Unless noted below, the Whispbook source code, documentation, and original
project assets in this repository are released under the MIT License above.

- Raster visual assets under docs/assets/ and src/assets/ were generated for
  Whispbook with OpenAI gpt-image-2 and are distributed as part of this project
  under the MIT License above. Use of the generation service and generated
  output remains subject to OpenAI's applicable terms.
- Bundled voice style presets under voice_styles/ include short normalized
  reference.wav clips derived from public-domain LibriVox audiobooks identified
  in README.md. The trimmed clips remain public domain; the JSON preset metadata
  is released under the MIT License above.
- TTS model weights are not redistributed by this repository. Kokoro,
  Chatterbox, and Chatterbox Turbo are downloaded from Hugging Face on demand
  and retain their upstream licenses: Apache-2.0 for hexgrad/Kokoro-82M, MIT for
  ResembleAI/chatterbox, and MIT for ResembleAI/chatterbox-turbo.
- Third-party software dependencies retain their own licenses.
